track.name: Villano Antillano: Bzrp Music Sessions, Vol. 51

wiki.summary: “Villano Antillano: BZRP Music Sessions, Vol. 51” is the fifth Bizarrap session featuring a Puerto Rican artist. In this case, she is the first woman of all the Puerto Rican participants. She is the second member of the LGBTQ+ community to work with the Argentinian producer, and the sixth of all sessions to feature a female lead. wiki.content: “Villano Antillano: BZRP Music Sessions, Vol. 51” is the fifth Bizarrap session featuring a Puerto Rican artist. In this case, she is the first woman of all the Puerto Rican participants. She is the second member of the LGBTQ+ community to work with the Argentinian producer, and the sixth of all sessions to feature a female lead. The song could be heard earlier by curious fans in a store in Madrid. The announcement of this song caused uncertainty since the Argentine producer apparently skipped the 50th edition of his famous Bizarrap Music Sessions, and also drew attention because many fans believed that the session was by Quevedo or C Tangana.
